1. Newly upgraded UI and interactive interface: simplified operation and enhanced user experience;
2. Detailed data display: allowing you to have the data from every inlet/outlet at your fingertips and better understand your power usage;
3. Customized use: the upper/lower battery level limits for charging/discharging, charging speed adjustment, car charging input current and standby time setting are customized to improve the use safety and flexibility;
4. Compatible with the latestly launched new products such as DELTA Max, DELTA Pro and DELTA mini.
